setDetails.setDescription:
MoonQuant’s DeFi + Mainstream Crypto set rebalances among Mainstream crypto assets (BTC, ETH, LINK), the DeFi Pulse Index (DeFi's most representative portfolio) and a stablecoin.

MQDMC's objective is to take advantage of efficient diversification strategies based on modern portfolio theory while maintaining positive exposure to crypto markets.

The MoonQuant algorithm analyzes multi-time frame indicators to determine market direction and position sizing. It is not a scalping bot, nor does it seek to catch tops and bottoms. It utilizes a proprietary signal awareness engine which seeks to determine best-performing and efficient rebalancing strategies.

MQDMC seeks to outperform indices (and ‘hodling’) while minimizing downside, always under the oversight of professional portfolio managers.

MQDMC is not a regulated investment vehicle and MoonQuant is not a regulated investment advisor. An investor may get back less than the amount invested.

Please note that MoonQuant or Token Sets reserve the right to amend the operation of the set.

FEES: In addition to streaming fee, this set will collect a performance fee equal to 10% of net gains, calculated per calendar month. These fees will be charged by rebalancing the fee amount into a FEES token, that will act as a fee collection mechanism.

THE RISK OF INVESTING IN CRYPTOCURRENCIES OR CRYPTO RELATED ASSETS IS SUBSTANTIAL AND CAN RESULT IN A COMPLETE LOSS OF FUNDS. INVESTORS SHOULD CAREFULLY CONSIDER WHETHER SUCH AN INVESTMENT IS SUITABLE FOR THEM IN LIGHT OF THEIR FINANCIAL CONDITION. INVESTORS SHOULD SEEK INDEPENDENT, PROFESSIONAL LEGAL, TAX & INVESTMENT ADVICE. PAST PERFORMANCE IS NOT INDICATIVE OF FUTURE RESULTS.
setDetails.managerDescription: MoonQuant Capital is a probabilistic multi-crypto asset manager that specializes in algorithmic, systematic trading strategies.
